ZH: 雪花飘落在大地上。
EN: Snowflakes are falling on the ground.

ZH: 这片雪花有多美丽啊！
EN: How beautiful this snowflake is!

ZH: 孩子们在雪地里捕捉雪花。
EN: The children are catching snowflakes in the snow.

ZH: 雪花覆盖了整个城市。
EN: The snowflakes covered the entire city.

ZH: 在寒冷的冬天，雪花给人们带来欢乐。
EN: In the cold winter, snowflakes bring joy to people.

ZH: 我们用雪花做成一个大雪人。
EN: We made a big snowman out of snowflakes.

ZH: 雪花在漫天飞舞，像是给大地铺上了绒毯。
EN: The snowflakes danced in the sky, like a blanket covering the earth.

ZH: 雪花在阳光下闪闪发光。
EN: The snowflakes sparkled in the sunlight.

ZH: 雄伟的山脉上一片雪花皑皑。
EN: The majestic mountains are covered in snowflakes.

ZH: 窗外的雪花透过玻璃，看起来纷纷扬扬。
EN: The snowflakes outside the window look fluttering through the glass.

ZH: 小溪旁边的树枝上挂满了雪花。
EN: The branches next to the creek are covered with snowflakes.

ZH: 我把一个个雪花放在手心里仔细观察。
EN: I put each snowflake in my palm and observed them carefully.

ZH: 在纷纷扬扬的雪花中，我们驱车前行。
EN: Among the falling snowflakes, we drive forward.

ZH: 雪花的形状各不相同。
EN: Each snowflake has a different shape.

ZH: 雪花落在树叶上，使它们变得洁白无瑕。
EN: Snowflakes fall on the leaves, making them pure and flawless.

ZH: 我们用扩大镜观察雪花的细节。
EN: We observed the details of the snowflake through a magnifying glass.

ZH: 时间像雪花一样悄悄地飞逝。
EN: Time flies quietly like snowflakes.

ZH: 纷纷扬扬的雪花让冬天变得更加美丽。
EN: The fluttering snowflakes make winter more beautiful.

ZH: 在大雪纷飞的日子里，雪花越来越大。
EN: On snowy days, the snowflakes get bigger and bigger.

ZH: 我们堆了一座由雪花组成的雪堆。
EN: We made a snow pile composed of snowflakes.
